{"tid":448552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞賊油麻地偷生果用鎅刀傷人被捕","createTime":"2017-10-26T10:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T10:48:46.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0f3ac5fc754ca28719d19e0e075b9f13631e2dfd","tid":448552,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:14:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171026/photo/bkn-20171026133721370-1026_00822_001_01p.jpg?20171026171932\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171026%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171026133721370-1026_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20171026171932&h=38577f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">巴籍漢(左)涉偷生果(右)及傷人被捕。</span><br />\n<br />\n南亞賊油麻地偷生果傷人被捕。下午1時許，一名巴基斯坦男子途經新填地街一生果檔，隨手攞起一個番石榴，未有付款便放落口食，姓張檔主發現追問，雙方發生激烈糾纏，期間張不慎撞向一輛手推車，致腳傷「拗柴」，巴漢見狀即拔足逃走。<br />\n<br />\n適時，對面雞蛋檔一名姓鄧檔主見狀，即協助追截，雙方跑約百米至渡船街及西貢街交界，巴籍漢遭追及與鄧肉搏，混亂間有人取出一把鎅刀施襲，鄧猝不及防左前臂中刀，巴籍漢隨即脫下外套赤膊逃走，多名街坊此時尾隨大嗌「捉賊」，有人協助報警。<br />\n<br />\n巴籍漢逃至約200米外近文匯街，一隊機動部隊警員接報趕至，迅即將疑犯制服。事件中2名檔主受傷，需送院治理，現場遺下血漬及牛仔褸。警方初步調查後，以涉嫌盜竊及傷人，將該名巴籍漢拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171026/bkn-20171026133721370-1026_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171026%2Fbkn-20171026133721370-1026_00822_001.html&d=Y7VwzlJytDCaiwRAYbw4aTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=4fd78f60\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171026/bkn-20171026133721370-1026_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fcc62bdafa575465625ded780def5c0aa887592b","tid":448552,"uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:15:09.000Z","msg":"南亞狗又拎一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e683d759377aac6c7be8e83b105b5d7782ffc7","tid":448552,"uid":136455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:16:36.000Z","msg":"一日一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有上報"},{"pid":"1719ee15fed7762390ff1b2ff72c38b6ecf02438","tid":448552,"uid":136455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:17:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一日一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上報</blockquote>"},{"pid":"126656603b7bca6506bb3cf09ec272c1af258d71","tid":448552,"uid":87511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:41:10.000Z","msg":"如果張超雄唔出嚟賠兩位檔主嘅醫藥費,就唔好怪人狙擊佢啦"},{"pid":"16478fc7ca0c59e0e39c381427c93cb08146f69b","tid":448552,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:47:08.000Z","msg":"蝻亞裔靠雙手打出一片天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n值得支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4b8659d21f8dae71223cc05fa02c3662275adb","tid":448552,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:48:46.000Z","msg":"順便反蝗反蝻一齊反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}